<div id="header" ><a href="http://economix.blogs.nytimes.com/" title="Go to Economix Home"><img src="http://graphics8.nytimes.com/images/blogs_v3/economix/economix_post.png" alt="Economix - Explaining the Science of Everyday Life"/></a></div><!-- END #blogHeader --><hr />
